note.p:
Compare the different wording in Bkaḥ-ḥgyur, Dkon-brtsegs, I. 1 and
                                II. 2 (pp. 16-17). Inthe 7th ḥdus-pa (bdun not mdun) is II. 2;
                                the 43rd leḥu would be VI. 95, the Kāśyapa parivarta.

